cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.Distributed, cs.PL, cs.AR. 

The paper discusses serverless cloud computing, which is a distributed computing paradigm. Therefore, cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses the simplification of cloud programming, which falls under cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also discusses the evolution of programming languages, which falls under cs.PL (Programming Languages). The paper also discusses applications that stretch the current limits of serverless, which falls under cs.AR (Augmented Reality and Virtual Reality).
